text: Eunidia wittei is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1940. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Eunidia wittei. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1940
